Prudential do Brasil Seguros de Vida (Brazil)

Headquartered in Rio de Janeiro, Prudential do Brasil Seguros de Vida was established in September 1997 as a joint venture with Bradesco Seguros. In 2002, it became a fully owned subsidiary of Prudential Financial, Inc. Prudential do Brasil introduced the innovative Life Planner® concept in Brazil with a strong commitment to superior customer service.  The company’s sales professionals specialize in family protection, providing customers with personalized protection life insurance through needs-based selling.

Prudential do Brasil Seguros de Vida S.A.
