Prudential Real Estate Investors Investimentos Imobiliarios Ltda

PREI has been investing in Latin America since 2000. We currently manage funds specializing in industrial, residential, and retail properties in Mexico and Brazil, and we have transactions capabilities in Mexico, Brazil, Argentina, and Chile.

Representative presence in Rio De Janeiro

